"directly in the class, not in any method of the class. A property is a "
"class attribute that will automatically create instance attributes. Each "
"property by default provides an ``on_<propertyname>`` event that is "
"called whenever the property's state/value changes."
msgstr ""
"それらを使用するには、** クラスレベルで宣言する必要があります。"
